 computation.\n\nThe style resolution pipeline flows through ServoStyleSet as the orchestrator, which coordinates with RestyleManager for change tracking and schedules restyling via the Servo engine through FFI bindings in ServoBindings. ServoUtils provides the thread-safety and traversal state infrastructure needed for this async style computation."
